{"name":"教程","postlist":[{"title":"Windows远程桌面docker容器","slug":"Windows远程桌面Linux","date":"2021-10-10T07:23:42.000Z","updated":"2021-10-14T12:27:26.195Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Windows远程桌面Linux.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":"苏逸,Wans,Wans小木屋,笔记,博客","cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/jerryc127/CDN@latest/cover/default_bg.png","content":"<p>编写Dockerfile文件（可选择dokcer文件，我没测试）</p>\n<p>（Windows无法连通docker容器所以这是Linux中做的实验）</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">FROM centos</span><br><span class=\"line\">MAINTAINER Wans&lt;wa.ns@qq.com&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">ENV MYPATH /sbin/init</span><br><span class=\"line\">WORKDIR $MYPATH</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN yum -y install vim</span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN yum -y install net-tools</span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN rpm -Uvh https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm</span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN yum -y install xrdp</span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN systemctl start xrdp</span><br><span class=\"line\">RUN systemctl enable xrdp</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">CMD echo $MYPATH</span><br><span class=\"line\">CMD echo &quot;----end----&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>1、放行3389端口，重启防火墙</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">firewall-cmd --permanent --zone=public --add-port=3389/tcp</span><br><span class=\"line\">firewall-cmd --reload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>2、运行docker centos容器</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">docker run -it -p 3389:3389 -p 3350:3350 --privileged true --name mycentos centos /sbin/init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>3、安装xrdp、vim、net-tools</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum -y install vim</span><br><span class=\"line\">yum -y install net-tools</span><br><span class=\"line\">rpm -Uvh https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/epel/epel-release-latest-7.noarch.rpm</span><br><span class=\"line\">yum -y install xrdp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>启动xrdp</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">systemctl start xrdp</span><br><span class=\"line\">systemctl enable xrdp</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>打开Windows远程连接就好</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211010160758852.png\" alt=\"image-20211010160758852\"></p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"教程","path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}]},{"title":"Windows10网络感叹号修复","slug":"Windows10网络感叹号修复","date":"2021-10-11T08:27:19.000Z","updated":"2021-12-06T06:07:12.736Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Windows10网络感叹号修复.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":"苏逸,Wans,Wans小木屋,笔记,博客","cover":"https://asuhe.jp/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/screenshot-1024x768.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"Windows10-修复网络感叹号bug\"><a href=\"#Windows10-修复网络感叹号bug\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Windows10 修复网络感叹号bug\"></a>Windows10 修复网络感叹号bug</h1><blockquote>\n<p>修复连接显示无internet但是有网的bug，链接在下方</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211011162902502.png\" alt=\"image-20211011162902502\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>打开这个工具，点击一键修复，然后重启就好了</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211011163154911.png\" alt=\"image-20211011163154911\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211011163441976.png\" alt=\"image-20211011163441976\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"windows10网络修复工具下载链接（阿里云）\"><a href=\"#windows10网络修复工具下载链接（阿里云）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"windows10网络修复工具下载链接（阿里云）\"></a><a href=\"https://www.aliyundrive.com/s/BcyXmzrxPWo\">windows10网络修复工具下载链接（阿里云）</a></h2><h2 id=\"蓝奏云链接\"><a href=\"#蓝奏云链接\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"蓝奏云链接\"></a><a href=\"https://syakj.lanzoui.com/irCHJv7sfxe\">蓝奏云链接</a></h2>","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"教程","path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"windows10","path":"api/tags/windows10.json"}]},{"title":"IntelliJ IDEA 2021.3、PyCharm永久激活","slug":"jetbrains","date":"2021-12-11T05:35:08.000Z","updated":"2021-12-11T06:57:26.897Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/jetbrains.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":"苏逸,Wans,Wans小木屋,笔记,博客","cover":"/images/jetbrains.png","content":"<h1 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#前言\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"前言\"></a>前言</h1><blockquote>\n<p>今天我安装PyCharm和IDEA的时候专业版的时候发现之前的激活方法已经失效了，于</p>\n<p>是，我花了两个小时在网上找到了。两种插件激活方法，这两种都是比较新的，</p>\n<p>第一个插件<code>FineAgent</code>（作者好像把这项目停了，但是还可以使用）</p>\n<p>第二种<code>ja-netfilter</code>Z大开发的（2021.11.30号发布） </p>\n<p>接下来我就以Z大的插件来写一个教程</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"注意：\"><a href=\"#注意：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"注意：\"></a>注意：</h1><p>我写这篇文章使用的idea和PyCharm版本是<code>2021.2.3</code></p>\n<p>链接都放最后</p>\n<h1 id=\"准备工作\"><a href=\"#准备工作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"准备工作\"></a>准备工作</h1><h2 id=\"将下载的插件解压\"><a href=\"#将下载的插件解压\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"将下载的插件解压\"></a>将下载的插件解压</h2><p>如果是在github下载的你是没有mymap-v1.0.jar这个文件的</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211211142549801.png\" alt=\"image-20211211142549801\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211211142623600.png\" alt=\"image-20211211142623600\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"修改配置文件\"><a href=\"#修改配置文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改配置文件\"></a>修改配置文件</h2><p>将下面的内容复制到janf_config.txt文件中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\">DNS</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">EQUAL,jetbrains.com</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\">URL</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">PREFIX,https://account.jetbrains.com/lservice/rpc/validateKey.action</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[<span class=\"string\">MyMap</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">EQUAL,licenseeName-&gt;Wans小木屋</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">EQUAL,gracePeriodDays-&gt;30</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">EQUAL,paidUpTo-&gt;5201-12-31</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"1、在jetbrains的官网下载并安装PyCharm或idea\"><a href=\"#1、在jetbrains的官网下载并安装PyCharm或idea\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1、在jetbrains的官网下载并安装PyCharm或idea\"></a>1、在jetbrains的官网下载并安装PyCharm或idea</h1><blockquote>\n<p>我已经安装好了</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211211140552241.png\" alt=\"image-20211211140552241\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211211135926682.png\" alt=\"image-20211211135926682\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"2、打开你要激活的软件（PyCharm）为例\"><a href=\"#2、打开你要激活的软件（PyCharm）为例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2、打开你要激活的软件（PyCharm）为例\"></a>2、打开你要激活的软件（PyCharm）为例</h1><p>点击开始试用</p>\n<p>如果不能试用那就输入激活码，<a href=\"https://jetbra.in/test-7b06e3ddfa68ff9b483adfcd08cdd243831f7928.html?t=16018385822\">获取临时激活码网址</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211211141453155.png\" alt=\"image-20211211141453155\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>临时激活成功，不要着急，现在才开始激活</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211211141656767.png\" alt=\"image-20211211141656767\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"3、配置软件VM（需要你创建这个文件）\"><a href=\"#3、配置软件VM（需要你创建这个文件）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3、配置软件VM（需要你创建这个文件）\"></a>3、配置软件VM（需要你创建这个文件）</h1><p>点击Help –&gt; Edit Custom VM Options （我这里汉化了勉强截个图）</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211211142106472.png\" alt=\"image-20211211142106472\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>然后添加以下内容<br>注意路径要写你的路径，记得替换以下斜杠<br>不要有什么中文路径，特殊符号什么的。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">-javaagent:D:/JetBrains/janetfilter/ja-netfilter.jar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211211142320150.png\" alt=\"image-20211211142320150\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>重启软件，重新点击试用</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211211141453155.png\" alt=\"image-20211211141453155\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>成功激活</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"/images/image-20211211144613630.png\" alt=\"image-20211211144613630\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"参考大神\"><a href=\"#参考大神\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考大神\"></a>参考大神</h1><p><a href=\"https://zhile.io/\">Z大(知了)</a></p>\n","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"教程","path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"激活","path":"api/tags/激活.json"},{"name":"ider","path":"api/tags/ider.json"},{"name":"Pycharm","path":"api/tags/Pycharm.json"},{"name":"jetbrains","path":"api/tags/jetbrains.json"}]},{"title":"windows装mysql解压版教程","slug":"windows装mysql解压版","date":"2021-10-27T09:12:08.000Z","updated":"2021-12-06T06:07:35.934Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/windows装mysql解压版.json","excerpt":null,"keywords":"苏逸,Wans,Wans小木屋,笔记,博客","cover":"https://asuhe.jp/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/screenshot-1024x768.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"安装\"><a href=\"#安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装\"></a>安装</h1><ul>\n<li><p>用<strong>管理员</strong>打开CMD，切换到MySql的解压目录下的<code>bin</code>目录：</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>执行以下命令</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 执行这里会生成，记住这个密码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">mysqld --initialize --console</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 安装mysql服务</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">mysqld -install</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> windows</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">mysqld.exe --initialize --console</span><br><span class=\"line\">mysqld.exe -install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ul>\n<li><p>输入命令<code>net start mysql</code>或<code>sc start mysql</code>启动mysql服务</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>输入<code>mysql -u root -p</code>来登陆数据库，并输入前面记录的临时密码：</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>登陆成功后输入以下命令<code>a</code>将原来复杂的密码修改为自己的密码，并输入<code>commit;</code>提交：</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n <figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/*1、修改密码*/</span><br><span class=\"line\">alter user &#x27;root&#x27;@&#x27;localhost&#x27; identified by &#x27;想要设置的密码&#x27;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">/*2、由于mysql 8.0*修改加密方式，使用下面命令可以解决大部分无法连接数据库命令*/</span><br><span class=\"line\">ALTER USER &#x27;root&#x27;@&#x27;localhost&#x27; IDENTIFIED BY &#x27;1&#x27; PASSWORD EXPIRE NEVER;</span><br><span class=\"line\">/*3、MySQL8.0的caching_sha2_password问题*/</span><br><span class=\"line\">ALTER USER root@localhost IDENTIFIED WITH mysql_native_password BY &#x27;1&#x27;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">FLUSH PRIVILEGES;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<ul>\n<li>在mysql的目录下设置配置文件my.ini</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[mysqld] </span><br><span class=\"line\"># 设置mysql的安装目录，也就是刚才我们解压的目录</span><br><span class=\"line\">basedir=D:/Program Files/mysql/mysql-8.0.27-winx64</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 设置mysql数据库的数据的存放目录</span><br><span class=\"line\"># datadir=D:/Program Files/mysql/mysql-8.0.27-winx64/data</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 设置默认使用的端口</span><br><span class=\"line\">port=3306</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 允许最大连接数</span><br><span class=\"line\">max_connections=200</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 允许连接失败的次数。这是为了防止有人试图攻击数据库</span><br><span class=\"line\">max_connect_errors=10</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 服务端使用的字符集</span><br><span class=\"line\">character-set-server=utf8mb4</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 数据库字符集对应一些排序等规则使用的字符集</span><br><span class=\"line\">collation-server=utf8mb4_general_ci</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 创建新表时将使用的默认存储引擎</span><br><span class=\"line\">default-storage-engine=INNODB</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 默认使用“mysql_native_password”插件作为认证加密方式</span><br><span class=\"line\"># MySQL8.0默认认证加密方式为caching_sha2_password</span><br><span class=\"line\">default_authentication_plugin=mysql_native_password</span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\">[mysql]</span><br><span class=\"line\"># 设置mysql客户端默认字符集</span><br><span class=\"line\">default-character-set=utf8mb4</span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\">[client]</span><br><span class=\"line\">default-character-set=utf8mb4</span><br><span class=\"line\">port=3306</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h1 id=\"卸载\"><a href=\"#卸载\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"卸载\"></a>卸载</h1><figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/*删除mysql*/</span><br><span class=\"line\">taskkill /f /t /im mysqld.exe</span><br><span class=\"line\">sc delete mysql</span><br><span class=\"line\">/*停止MySQL服务*/</span><br><span class=\"line\">net stop mysqld 或者 sc stop mysqld</span><br><span class=\"line\">/*删除MySQL服务*/</span><br><span class=\"line\">sc delete mysqld 或 mysqld -remove（需先停止服务）</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","raw":null,"categories":[{"name":"教程","path":"api/categories/教程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"环境搭建","path":"api/tags/环境搭建.json"}]}]}